Ministers who serve in the National Coronavirus Command Council, have briefed the media on the regulations relating to the COVID-19 Level 3 restrictions. This follows the announcements made by President Cyril Ramaphosa on Sunday, 24 May 2020, and the subsequent address to the nation on Tuesday, 26 May 2020 where in the president spoke about the opening of places of worship under level 3. The media briefing is accessible below: 